name: Negligence
description:
This artwork was inspired by historical esoteric iconography and the artwork found on tarot cards. Negligence is infused with spiritual intuition and was intentionally designed to be used as a tool in divination. This card represents the concept of negligence; various interpretations are possible.

Mixed Media: Prismacolor and Procreate
Dimensions: 2607x3367
Resolution: 300x300
